Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.02,0:00:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,NG Voice Drama: The Black Demon's End
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.56,0:00:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,This is one possibility, the crossing of two fates...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.94,0:00:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,and the ending that lies ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.68,0:00:38.94,Default,Yashiki,0,0,0,,"Shit, I took too long getting prepared! Make it in time,\Nplease...!"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.10,0:00:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I was driving to Kissoji from the Kujou Mansion. Right now,\Nit's past 8 P.M.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.86,0:00:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's summertime, but the sky's already pitch black.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.36,0:00:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It all started with a report from Rose.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.38,0:01:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,She was a friend of my late sister, Saya, and helps me in my\Ninvestigations.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.20,0:01:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,After delivering her report on Kakuya's Game, she asked me\Nto help save a boy named Akira Kijima in her stead.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.20,0:01:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way I could ignore the situation after hearing\Nher story. I got ready and headed off to Kissoji.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.74,0:01:55.72,Default,Yashiki,0,0,0,,"(The Black Rabbit... Kijima's supposed to be here.)"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.26,0:01:59.22,Default,Yashiki,0,0,0,,"Urgh...!"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.22,0:02:06.14,Default,Yashiki,0,0,0,,"(It reeks of blood... I'm too late.)"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.14,0:02:12.32,Spirit,Tentacle-Armed Man,0,0,0,SpiritBG,"Agh... Augh... Uaargh..."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.32,0:02:19.00,Default,Yashiki,0,0,0,,"Are you Akira Kijima? The people collapsed at your feet\Nare your aunt and little sister, aren't they?"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.00,0:02:24.20,Default,Yashiki,0,0,0,,"Were you the one that did that to them? With that\Ntentacle-like arm of yours...?"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.00,0:02:31.84,Default,Yashiki,0,0,0,,"I sympathize with your fate. Rose did too."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.84,0:02:38.02,Default,Yashiki,0,0,0,,"She wasn't lying. She really wanted to save you!"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.02,0:02:43.34,Default,Yashiki,0,0,0,,"But your Bloodmetry was even stronger than she could have\Nanticipated."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.34,0:02:48.04,Default,Yashiki,0,0,0,,"She was able to save your life, but your power ran wild\Nin the process."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.04,0:02:51.98,Default,Yashiki,0,0,0,,"It destroyed both your memories and your humanity!"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.98,0:02:57.94,Default,Yashiki,0,0,0,,"As a result, you're still alive, but your mind and body\Nbecame those of a spirit."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.94,0:03:01.02,Default,Yashiki,0,0,0,,"With things like this, I can't let you be."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.02,0:03:06.92,Spirit,Akira,0,0,0,,"Agh... Augh...."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.92,0:03:10.80,Default,Yashiki,0,0,0,,"Unfortunately, my words don't seem to be reaching you."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.80,0:03:14.64,Default,Yashiki,0,0,0,,"I really wish we could've met in a different way."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.64,0:03:19.08,Default,Yashiki,0,0,0,,"Forgive me, Akira Kijima."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.08,0:03:24.24,Default,Yashiki,0,0,0,,"I've already looked into you, so I've come prepared."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.24,0:03:28.88,Default,Yashiki,0,0,0,,"Even if my voice can't reach you, this song should!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.88,0:03:36.58,Default,Boombox,0,0,0,,"Under the clouds, looking for the stars..."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.58,0:03:38.86,Spirit,Akira,0,0,0,,"Aaugh...!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.86,0:03:42.06,Default,Yashiki,0,0,0,,"Remember Kaoru Hazuki! Remember her death!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.06,0:03:46.00,Default,Yashiki,0,0,0,,"Next up is this can of juice!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.52,0:03:50.90,Spirit,Akira,0,0,0,,"Augh...!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.90,0:03:58.14,Default,Yashiki,0,0,0,,"How about that weirdly named juice?! Did it jog your\Nmemory about Seiji Amanome's death?!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.14,0:04:01.54,Default,Yashiki,0,0,0,,"I know it's difficult, but you have to remember, Akira!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.54,0:04:06.18,Default,Yashiki,0,0,0,,"You can't escape the past by running away from your memories!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.18,0:04:11.10,Default,Yashiki,0,0,0,,"You have to face the truth to keep living!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.10,0:04:16.40,Default,Yashiki,0,0,0,,"If you can't do that, you'll be engulfed by your darkness and\Nbecome a real spirit!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.40,0:04:19.88,Default,Yashiki,0,0,0,,"Face the truth! There's no other choice!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.88,0:04:22.24,Default,Yashiki,0,0,0,,"I'll help you get through it!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.24,0:04:28.14,Spirit,Akira,0,0,0,,"Ha...zuki...? Ama...nome...?"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.14,0:04:32.96,Spirit,Akira,0,0,0,,"Uagh... UAAAGHH!!!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.96,0:04:37.22,Default,Yashiki,0,0,0,,"(Agh...! The tentacle's... wrapped around my neck...)"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.22,0:04:43.70,Default,Yashiki,0,0,0,,"(Let go of me... I can't... breathe...!)"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.48,0:04:48.52,Default,Yashiki,0,0,0,,"Augh..."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.52,0:04:52.86,Default,Mashita,0,0,0,,"Tch... You really know how to get into trouble, don't you?"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.86,0:04:59.90,Default,Mashita,0,0,0,,"But y'know, Yashiki... these lead bullets work just fine on\Nthese half-assed spirit wannabes."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.90,0:05:05.58,Default,Yashiki,0,0,0,,"Oh, Mashita...! Sorry about that, you really saved me."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.58,0:05:07.74,Default,Yashiki,0,0,0,,"But why are you here...?"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.74,0:05:16.02,Default,Mashita,0,0,0,,"Rose contacted me. Seems like that chick's mistaken me for\Nyour babysitter."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.02,0:05:20.84,Spirit,Akira,0,0,0,,"Augh... Aaauuggh...!"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.84,0:05:26.20,Default,Mashita,0,0,0,,"Looks like the little shit's back up on his feet. But his arm's\Nbeen shot. His movement's slowed."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.20,0:05:28.62,Default,Mashita,0,0,0,,"Hurry up and finish him off, Yashiki."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.62,0:05:35.88,Default,Yashiki,0,0,0,,"Yeah, I know. With the state he's in, he might take a proper\Nlook at this."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.78,0:05:41.38,Default,Yashiki,0,0,0,,"Akira, you remember this hand mirror, don't you?"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.38,0:05:45.68,Default,Yashiki,0,0,0,,"It's was your late mother Satomi's, wasn't it?"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.68,0:05:53.32,Default,Yashiki,0,0,0,,"Seems like Rose found it in your room. She gave it to me,\Nthinking it might come in handy."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.32,0:06:01.44,Default,Yashiki,0,0,0,,"She was afraid of what flowed through the Miroku family's\Nblood, hoping that you wouldn't encounter the same fate."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.44,0:06:07.02,Default,Yashiki,0,0,0,,"But her wish didn't come true. You couldn't escape from the\Ncurse running through your veins."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.02,0:06:10.48,Default,Yashiki,0,0,0,,"But your life's not over yet, is it?!"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.48,0:06:14.68,Default,Yashiki,0,0,0,,"Akira! Look into the mirror! Look at what you've become!"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.68,0:06:21.46,Default,Yashiki,0,0,0,,"And reject it! Your mother never wanted you to end up like this!"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.68,0:06:26.84,Spirit,Akira,0,0,0,,"Is... is that... me...?"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.84,0:06:34.12,Spirit,Akira,0,0,0,,"Augh... UUUAAAGGGHHH...!"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.14,0:06:46.20,Default,Mashita,0,0,0,,"Seems like he passed out from shock. Looks like we're\Nsafe for now."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.20,0:06:49.42,Default,Mashita,0,0,0,,"So Yashiki, what happens now?"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.42,0:06:57.48,Default,Yashiki,0,0,0,,"Hm... We'd be in trouble if anyone came here after hearing\Nthe gunshots. Let's grab Akira and get out of here."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.48,0:07:04.36,Default,Mashita,0,0,0,,"Got it. I'll contact the hospital. If we call them now, they\Nmight still make it."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.36,0:07:11.62,Default,Mashita,0,0,0,,"You drag the brat to the car."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.60,0:07:42.22,Default,Mashita,0,0,0,,"I'll drive, Yashiki. You stay in the back and treat his wounds.\NAfter all, you're good with dealing with brats, aren't you?"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.22,0:07:47.98,Default,Yashiki,0,0,0,,"Well, I'm better than you are, at least."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.00,0:08:15.86,Default,Yashiki,0,0,0,,"...and that does it."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.88,0:08:23.82,Default,Akira,0,0,0,,"Ugh... Where... am I...?"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.82,0:08:28.48,Default,Yashiki,0,0,0,,"Oh, you're finally awake, Akira. How's your arm?"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.48,0:08:33.26,Default,Yashiki,0,0,0,,"I just performed some first-aid with some bandages,\Nso don't move too much."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.26,0:08:35.26,Default,Yashiki,0,0,0,,"You might re-open the wound."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.94,0:08:40.12,Default,Akira,0,0,0,,"...Who are you?"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.12,0:08:45.24,Default,Yashiki,0,0,0,,"My name's Kazuo Yashiki. I'm something like a friend\Nof Rose's."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.24,0:08:54.60,Default,Akira,0,0,0,,"Wait, could you be the leader she was talking about?\NThe one that uses crazy methods to solve spirit cases?"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.60,0:09:01.10,Default,Yashiki,0,0,0,,"Ah, I guess so. That description of me is a bit concerning,\Nthough..."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.10,0:09:04.18,Default,Akira,0,0,0,,"I see."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.18,0:09:08.30,Default,Akira,0,0,0,,"I'm already a full-blown spirit."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.30,0:09:13.72,Default,Akira,0,0,0,,"Just look at this lame, squid-like right arm of mine."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.72,0:09:20.28,Default,Akira,0,0,0,,"Because of my arm, Ami and Aunt Natsumi..."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.28,0:09:28.06,Default,Yashiki,0,0,0,,"It's okay, Akira. They've been transported to the hospital.\NI'm sure they'll get better."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.06,0:09:35.08,Default,Akira,0,0,0,,"But still...! I tried to kill them! That's not something that\Ncan just be forgiven..."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.08,0:09:41.08,Default,Akira,0,0,0,,"Hey, gramps! Your job is to exterminate spirits, right?"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.08,0:09:48.42,Default,Akira,0,0,0,,"Then please... kill me."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.10,0:09:54.10,Default,Yashiki,0,0,0,,"...It's true that you've done something that can never be\Nforgiven."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.10,0:09:58.38,Default,Yashiki,0,0,0,,"It's a burden you'll have to bear and atone for for your\Nwhole life."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.38,0:10:02.30,Default,Yashiki,0,0,0,,"But still... you didn't let the darkness consume you."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.30,0:10:07.02,Default,Yashiki,0,0,0,,"You regained your humanity and came back to the light."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.02,0:10:16.50,Default,Yashiki,0,0,0,,"If so, my job isn't to exterminate you. It's to help you.\NI want to help ease your mind, even in the slightest."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.34,0:10:26.24,Default,Yashiki,0,0,0,,"But first, it's time to rest, Akira. You can think about what\Nyou'll do after you wake up."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.24,0:10:30.30,Default,Yashiki,0,0,0,,"When that time comes, I'll help you out, too."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.30,0:10:38.18,Default,Akira,0,0,0,,"Haha, you really are a nice person... but you're way too\Nnaive."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.32,0:10:58.76,Default,Yashiki,0,0,0,,"We're almost at the Kujou Mansion."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.76,0:11:02.58,Default,Mashita,0,0,0,,"Yashiki, is that brat asleep?"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.58,0:11:10.82,Default,Yashiki,0,0,0,,"Yeah. Both his body and mind are in shambles. It's best for him\Nto rest for now."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.82,0:11:15.06,Default,Mashita,0,0,0,,"Even though he just looks like a demon when he's asleep."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.06,0:11:20.72,Default,Mashita,0,0,0,,"So, what are you planning to do after bringing that kid home?"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.72,0:11:27.78,Default,Yashiki,0,0,0,,"I... want to do something to save him, Mashita."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.78,0:11:32.56,Default,Mashita,0,0,0,,"Don't tell me... you're seeing yourself in him, aren't you, Yashiki?"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.56,0:11:40.38,Default,Mashita,0,0,0,,"You both had your lives pulled around by spirits, losing your\Nfamily in the process. You two really are birds of a feather."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.38,0:11:43.02,Default,Yashiki,0,0,0,,"I can't deny my sympathy with him."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.02,0:11:49.14,Default,Yashiki,0,0,0,,"But we're not the same! His family's still alive."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.14,0:11:55.02,Default,Yashiki,0,0,0,,"If he's freed of his curse and has someone to support him,\Nhe might be able to go back to his normal life."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.02,0:11:56.54,Default,Yashiki,0,0,0,,"Don't you agree?!"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.54,0:12:01.26,Default,Mashita,0,0,0,,"Tch. Easy on the brats as always, huh?"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.26,0:12:05.94,Default,Mashita,0,0,0,,"Just like during the The Departed case."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.94,0:12:13.34,Default,Mashita,0,0,0,,"But Yashiki, don't forget this: he isn't a human anymore.\NHe's a spirit."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.34,0:12:22.46,Default,Mashita,0,0,0,,"The amount of darkness a spirit is burdened with is always\Nbeyond our wildest expectations. I'm sure you know that."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.46,0:12:32.16,Default,Mashita,0,0,0,,"Against all that darkness, that speck of reason he showed\Nyou doesn't stand a chance."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.16,0:12:36.00,Default,Yashiki,0,0,0,,"What are you trying to say, Mashita?!"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.00,0:12:39.96,Default,Mashita,0,0,0,,"You already know, don't you, Yashiki?"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.96,0:12:43.32,Default,Mashita,0,0,0,,"That brat's actually-"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.32,0:12:53.34,Default,Yashiki,0,0,0,,"You're wrong, Mashita. Remember why we're doing this\Nwork in the first place."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.34,0:13:01.58,Default,Mashita,0,0,0,,"...Yeah. You might be right."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.62,0:13:14.60,Spirit,Akira,0,0,0,,"AAAUUUGGHHH!!"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.60,0:13:19.74,Default,Mashita,0,0,0,,"You bastard! Let go of the handle!"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.74,0:13:21.70,Default,Yashiki,0,0,0,,"UUAAGGGHHH!"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.70,0:13:25.00,Default,Mashita,0,0,0,,"AAUUGGGHHHH!!!"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.00,0:13:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
